column14: Description
As a cashier, I need to add payment details into the restaurant ordering system, so that company can calculate total sales amount.
As a cashier, I need to add order into the restaurant ordering system, so that the company can keep track on customers' top preference food.
As a  restaurant manager, I want to manage restaurant staff so that restaurant can use the man power effectively and efficiency.
As a staff manager, I want to reserve customer seat so that customer don't have to take long queue when they dine in.
As a restaurant manager, i need to maintain member details. So that, restaurant is able to send promotion message and voucher to customer.
As a restaurant manager, I want to manage the food menu so that the restaurant is able to provide various food to customer.
As a cashier, I need to generate receipt, so that the company can keep track what had been sold to who.
As a cashier, I need to calculate total payment details, so that the receipt can be generated to the customer.
As a staff manager, I want to search customer reserved seat so that I can search any customer reserved seat that I want.
As a restaurant manager, i want to search member details. So that, i can save time for searching from large amount of member list.
As a restaurant manager, I want to search food details so that I can view the food details in more efficiency way.
As a restaurant manager, I want to search staff information, so that i can save time for searching from a large amount of staff list.
As a restaurant manager, I want to edit the food details in food menu so that I able to adjust the price of the food for business strategy purpose.
As a restaurant manager, I want delete the staff information, so that i do not waste time on the staff information that not longer work in restaurant.
As a cashier, I need to cancel ordered item from the restaurant ordering system, so that it provide flexibility to the customer.
As a restaurant manager, I want to retrieve staff information so that i can know the personal details of a  staff, no need to meet every staff to understand their personalities.
As a cashier, i need to add new order item into a single order receipt, so that customer order can be recorded.
As a restaurant manager, I want to view the food menu so that I able to view the details of the food.
As a restaurant manager, i want to delete member. So that,  is easy to keep track who is registered member.
As a restaurant manager, i want to check member details. So that, can analyze member behavior.
As a restaurant manager, I want to edit staff information so that I can get the update to date staff information.
As a staff manager, I want to check the reserved seat so that I can know whether the customer reserved the seat or no.
As a restaurant manage, I want to add a new staff information, so that i can assign task effectively according to the information.
